ays, Wednes\nday, Thursday and Friday, October 29, 30, 31. You may shop in any de-\ns. partment in the store at your leisure, in advance of the great day! Plan to\nshop any or all of the three days at Block and Kuhl\u2019s no one can afford\nto miss the savings offered! Six months of planning brings wanted, season\nable merchandise at lowest-pnces-of-the-year!\nSEE LARGE ADVERTISMENT\nFRIDAY, OCT. lit NEWS-TIMES\nL LOWE'S N\nSUITS\nfor\nAll of the Family\nFor The Youngsters\n4 to 12 years\nIncluded are Dutch Boy, Dutch Girl,\nPirate, Devil, Chinaman, Spanish,\nBlack Cat and Toy Soldier Costumes.\n98\nYoungsters Suits\nof the Better Grade\nSizes 4 to 16 1\n150 t0 $345\n.It-'\na t\nfVV:#/.\nAdult Suits\nLarge Variety of Costumes. Sizes to 44.\n$1.95 to $4.45\nMAX ADLER\nON THE CORNER\nMICHIGAN AND WASHINGTON","height":"32500","width":"24208"}}
